with turtle graphics
	'space' : turtle space in (the graphics panel)
	TURTLE : a turtle
	TURTLE’s  'speed' : 400
	place TURTLE in 'space'
	for each ('size') from 10 to 300 in steps of 10 
		square of size 'size'

square of size 'size' :
	'turtle' : TURTLE
	'turtle'’s 'speed' ↲
	TURTLE’s 'colour' : random colour
	repeat 4 times
		move TURTLE 'size' steps
		turn TURTLE 90 degrees
